channel.title: Run server error
channel.description:
hmm i just moved my server to a new pc, and i get this error on opening hte run server
[code] ... i cant copy it... well it sais sumthin like exxeption in thread "main" java.lang.noClassDefFoundError: server [/code]
ok so ne1 know wats rong?? i just updated jdk and jre on this pc to v 6, i did it on the old one and got that error be4 i put jre on, i got it on though and i am getting it so i have no idea what is wrong....[br][size=1]Posted on: February 18, 2007, 10:15:40 PM[/size][hr]I figured it out, for sum reason the shortcut was running wrong, i just remade it now it almost all works so u can delete this now.
